111	        <div class="lang-glyph-section">
112	            <h4>{"Operators (by Valence)"}</h4>
113	            <p class="lang-glyph-note">
114	                {"APL operators have different meanings depending on valence (number of arguments). \
115	                   1 arg = monadic (prefix), 2 args = dyadic (infix)."}
116	            </p>
117	            <div class="lang-glyph-scroll">
